    
    0.01_99 - 2011-03-24 - Release Candidate

o Use File::Temp to create temporal files in tests and daily usage.

    0.01_90 - 2011-03-20 - Beta release.

o Do not use /tmp in tests.
o Quote '$' in regexps supplied by the User.
o When both 'ask' and 'pretend' used, 'ask' wins.
o Recipe for changing version in Perl modules added.


    0.01_50 - 2011-03-18 - Alpha release.

o Initial implementation of essential functionality.

